    "body_html": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;caption-side:bottom;border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-sizing:border-box;border-collapse:collapse;&#10;              background-color: #f2f2f2; margin: 0; padding: 0;\" data-oe-version=\"1.0\">\n  <tbody style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:solid;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-left-color:inherit;border-bottom-color:inherit;border-right-color:inherit;border-top-color:inherit;\">\n    <tr style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:solid;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-left-color:inherit;border-bottom-color:inherit;border-right-color:inherit;border-top-color:inherit;\">\n      <td align=\"center\" style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:solid;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-left-color:inherit;border-bottom-color:inherit;border-right-color:inherit;border-top-color:inherit;padding:20px 0;\">\n        <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"600\" style=\"border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-collapse:collapse;caption-side:bottom;border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;&#10;                      max-width:600px; background-color:#ffffff; color:#101820; &#10;                      font-family:'Roboto',sans-serif; font-size:13px; line-height:1.6;\">\n          <tbody style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:solid;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-left-color:inherit;border-bottom-color:inherit;border-right-color:inherit;border-top-color:inherit;\">\n            <tr style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:solid;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-left-color:inherit;border-bottom-color:inherit;border-right-color:inherit;border-top-color:inherit;\">\n              <td style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:solid;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-left-color:inherit;border-bottom-color:inherit;border-right-color:inherit;border-top-color:inherit;padding:20px;\">\n\n                <p style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;margin:0; padding:0; font-size:13px;\">\n                  Dear Applicant,\n                  <br/><br/>\n                  Thank you for your interest in joining the <b style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;font-weight:bolder;\">BICC</b> team.\n                  Unfortunately, we noticed that you did not complete the required assessment \n                  as part of the application process. As a result, we have marked your application as refused.\n                  <br/><br/>\n                </p>\n\n                <p style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;margin:0; padding:0; font-size:13px;\">\n                  We understand that unforeseen circumstances can arise, \n                  and we want to assure you that this decision does not reflect on your professional capabilities.\n                </p>\n\n                <p style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;margin:0; padding:0; font-size:13px;\">\n                  If you believe this was a misunderstanding or encountered issues completing \n                  the assessment, please reply to this email. We would be happy to reconsider \n                  your application upon completion of the assessment.\n                </p>\n\n                <p style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;margin:0; padding:0; font-size:13px;\">\n                  We will also keep your resume on file for future opportunities \n                  that align with your skills and experience.\n                </p>\n\n                <p style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;margin:0; padding:0; font-size:13px;\">\n                  We appreciate your understanding and wish you the best in your job search.\n                </p>\n                <br/>\n\n                \n                <p style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;margin:0; padding:0; font-size:13px;\">\n                  Best regards,<br/>\n                  The Recruitment Team<br/>\n                  BICC<br/>\n                  <span style=\"color: #374151;\">https://www.bicc.ph</span>\n                </p>\n\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n          </tbody>\n        </table>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n",
